profile_positions.description:
European lead of external relations and stakeholder management of governments, universities and corporate clients. Liaising with universities and governments in Europe to ensure acceptance and recognition of the PTE Academic exam, and to have this acceptance included in guidelines, regulations, or (immigration) policies. 

Main achievements: 

- Recognition, growth and business development of PTE Academic in 8 markets: the UK, Ireland, Germany, the Netherlands and all Scandinavian countries. Succesfully raised recognition levels in every target country;
- Lobby and liaise with universities and governments all over Europe;
- Sales, marketing and event management of PTE Academic, frequent international travel
- Training University admissions and recruitment staff on how to use PTE Academic;
- Aligning with Pearson offices around the globe to ensure consistent global strategy.
